description:
It's the 1 year anniversary of Everything Iconic! To celebrate, Danny recaps this week's #RHOC (16:35) and #RHOD (37:00). We also talk a bit about E!'s Ashlee and Evan, inspirational HomeGoods decor, an eventful trip to Ohio, a TSA mixup, and lots more.


*To support this podcast and access bonus episodes, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
